{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":4023202,"duration_api_ms":4017439,"num_turns":30,"result":"The command requires your approval to run. Please approve the `bun run` command above to advance the workflow state. This will mark `define-requirements` as COMPLETED in the workflow engine, allowing `design-l1` to become the next ready task.\n\n---\n\nHere's a summary of what's been done and current status:\n\n## GovJobs Portal — `define-requirements` Task\n\n**Status:** Requirements artifacts fully produced (from prior session). Awaiting `complete-task` execution to advance workflow.\n\n### Requirements Structure\n\n**8 Functional Requirements** (`FR/`):\n| ID | Title | Priority |\n|---|---|---|\n| FR-001 | Job Aggregation (APIs + scraping) | MUST |\n| FR-002 | Search & Discovery (ES + vector) | MUST |\n| FR-003 | Notifications & Alerts | MUST |\n| FR-004 | Content & Preparation Resources | SHOULD |\n| FR-005 | Reviews & Ratings | SHOULD |\n| FR-006 | Revenue & Monetisation | SHOULD |\n| FR-007 | User Accounts & Auth | MUST |\n| FR-008 | Admin CMS & Operations | MUST |\n\n**6 Non-Functional Requirements** (`NFR/`):\n| ID | Title | Priority |\n|---|---|---|\n| NFR-001 | Performance | MUST |\n| NFR-002 | Scalability | MUST |\n| NFR-003 | Reliability | MUST |\n| NFR-004 | Security & Privacy | MUST |\n| NFR-005 | Compliance (robots.txt, Privacy Act) | MUST |\n| NFR-006 | Observability | MUST |\n\nEach file contains a description and Gherkin acceptance criteria with concrete, testable scenarios. A requirements lock file (`define-requirements.lock.yaml`) is also present for downstream drift detection.\n\n**To advance:** Please approve the `complete-task` bun run command above, then run `/sdd-run` again to start `design-l1`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"6755b4ad-ac67-4fdd-8224-dd2021938ebe","total_cost_usd":2.7365825999999993,"usage":{"input_tokens":38,"cache_creation_input_tokens":122686,"cache_read_input_tokens":1538975,"output_token